# Xcode
#
# gitignore contributors: remember to update Global/Xcode.gitignore, Objective-C.gitignore & Swift.gitignore

## User settings
xcuserdata/

## Scripts
*.3sc

## Build results
build/
DerivedData/

## Patterns to ignore
*.mode1v3
*.mode2v3
*.perspectivev3
!default.mode1v3
!default.mode2v3
!default.perspectivev3
*.xcuserstate

## Dependency manager
Pods/
Carthage/Build/
.build/

## Miscellaneous
*.moved-aside
*.ipa
*.dmg
*.log

## Swift Package Manager
.swiftpm/xcode/

## macOS
.DS_Store
